heading: EntreVerse
details: A plethora of exciting learning experiences await to take you into the realm of innovation as Entrepreneurship Cell, IIT Kanpur announces the first edition of EntreVerse: The Multiverse of Innovation from 19th-21st March 2022.

heading: Inter IIT Tech Meet 10.0
details: As the 10th Inter IIT Tech Meet is going to be organized online by IIT Kharagpur from 25th to 27th March 2022, we invite the campus community to participate in the Students' Academic Conference.

heading: Music Club's Official Merchandise
details: After a long wait, the official Music Club T-Shirts are finally out! Take this chance to show your love for music to the world and let people know you're a part of Music Club, IIT Kanpur!

heading: Altair Data Analysis Challenge
details: Techkriti, in association with Altair, is organizing a Data Analytics Challenge, specifically focussed on the student body of IIT Kanpur.
